PPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7806972616003740", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8696080173759642"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1172603213910493"}]}, "change_log": "Updates for Version 1.08.112:\n\nAdded two new more complex practice opponents: one left-handed and one right-handed. \n\nThe default pistol grip foil now has a more detailed blade with wire grove, tip tape and proper tip.\n\nAdded several new weapons models in the game that can be earned by winning competition bouts:\n *A French grip foil\n *A Italian grip foil\n *A French grip figure eight foil\n *A saber (the modern fencing kind)\n *A French grip epee.\n *A pistol grip epee.   (sorry, despite the epees and saber, still only a foil fencing game)\n\nOnce earned, your weapons can be changed by selecting from the wooden weapon stands on the back wall while \nthe game is displaying the selection menu at the end of the opponent's side of the strip. \n\nAdjust controller footwork speed to match your real footwork speed. You will have to advance and retreat the fencing piste while the game times you. \n\nYou can now adjust your weapon/VR controller offset. This has many possible uses:\n  *Simply adjust weapon/hand placement to your liking. \n  *Allows you to use a real fencing grip attachment to your controller. (Sorry I don't sell these attachments, you will have to build one yourself)\n  *Pommeling a French grip like a epeeist.\n   \nSetting to allow your weapon blades to glow with priority(right-of-way) when fencing.\n\nLock out controller rotating/turning setting while fencing for better control.\n\nBUG FIX: When canting your blade, the bend no longer starts behind the guard.", "created_date": 1725704765, "id": "8648272295207097", "version": "1.08.112", "version_code": 112, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7806972616003740", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8696080173759642"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1172603213910493"}]}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1725444976, "id": "8626796024021391", "version": "1.08.111", "version_code": 111, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7806972616003740", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8696080173759642"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1172603213910493"}]}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1723891091, "id": "8518327771534884", "version": "1.07.110", "version_code": 110, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}